There is also help available on each active invocation.  Use
|CKBdhelp spells|000 to see the exact help-file names.

Your silver sickle also serves as a Druid profession tool.  You can use
it as a gardening spade for |CKBgather herbs|000, a mining pick for
|CKBmine ore|000, and a skinning knife for |CKBskin corpse|000.

